    "body": "#26201 removed `taproot` from `getdeploymentinfo` (not yet in a release, slated for v32), which it turns out Lnd relies on: https://github.com/lightningnetwork/lnd/pull/10683\r\n\r\nExpand the release doc note to recommend the same solution they used: check for `TAPROOT` in the `script_flags` array. This was added in v31.",
