      "body": "We only added the `script_flags` array in v31.0, so it may be a bit annoying for RPC clients to have to use `getdeploymentinfo` for v30 and older. Since #26201 isn't in a release yet, we could temporarily put \"taproot\" back under `deployments` with a deprecation notice. Perhaps that's useful if Lnd is not the only client with this issue (since they've already dealt with it).",
