      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "body": "script_flags was indeed added in 4577fb2b1e098c3f560b1ff50a37ebfef2af5f32 v31\r\n\r\nHowever, I don't understand why any client would need to check for taproot. Our own wallet and mempool [assumes](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/23512) that it is active since genesis, so what is different about lightning wallets that they'd assume otherwise?",
